  "pattern_statement_html": "<span style=\"color:#ff963e;\">Math depth</span> is the gap. Where the diagnostic gives strong evidence the plan trims review; where evidence is thin it protects full instruction. That’s exactly what stands between 920 and 1250, and it’s teachable.",
